<div id="pfef0" class="pf w21 h127" data-page-no="ef0"><div class="pc pcef0 w21 h127"><div class="t m3bb x4e h16 y9a1 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE THIRTEENTH SABBATH OFFERING </div><div class="t mbd x29 h27 y156e ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">June 28 is the time for the next thirteenth Sabbath </div><div class="t m656 x26 h27 y4ad ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">offering. The General Conference Committee has re-</div><div class="t m429 x26 h27 yf7e ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">quested that this offeringbe used for sanitarium work </div><div class="t m9da x26 h27 yf6e ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in India. Remember that in India 300,000,000 souls, </div><div class="t m7c9 x26 h27 ya6a ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">about one fifth of the world&apos;s population, are sitting in </div><div class="t maf0 x26 h27 ya4a ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the darkness of heathenism. This call is a most urgent </div><div class="t m86b x26 h27 y1623 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">one, and our response should be liberal. </div><div class="t m856 x29 h27 yf8b ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Special Offering, June 28, 1913, for sanitarium work </div><div class="t m6b2 x26 h27 y5a2 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in India. Remember India&apos;s 300,000,000 souls. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
